paytable5_t02:
All wins are paid when a symbol matches a payline pattern from the leftmost side of the reels.
The prize value is the sum stacked per line, multiplied by the applicable prize multiplier as advertised on the paytable of the game. 
Where multiple wins occur on multiple win lines, the total win values are summed.
If more than one win occurs on the same payline, the largest win is paid. 
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

paytable6_rules:
TROPICAL GOLD is a 3-reel, 3-row, 5-line slot featuring RANDOM BONUS, FREE GAMES and RANDOM MULTIPLIER.
This game is played with 5 fixed bet lines and different bet levels.
RANDOM BONUS feature randomly appears and position a Bonus Wild symbol in the center of the reels which can trigger extra win combinations.
FREE GAMES feature triggers a random number of up to 5 FREE GAMES per every spin.
The FREE GAMES reel is to the left side of the main reels.
RANDOM MULTIPLIER feature can randomly net your win combination up to x25.
The RANDOM MULTIPLIER reel is to the right side of the main reels.
